sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as Host API
    participant Prep as RunPreparation
    participant Router as Intent Router
    participant Mem as Memory Orchestrator
    participant Planner as Planner
    participant Exec as Executor
    participant Obs as Event Store
    participant Persist as Long-term Memory

    U->>API: /api/agent/run or /api/agentstream/run
    API->>Prep: Create run and prepare input
    Prep->>Router: Classify intents
    Router-->>Prep: RetrievalPlan
    Prep->>Obs: intent_classified
    Prep->>Obs: retrieval_plan_built
    Prep->>Mem: Retrieve short/working/facts/profile/vector
    Mem->>Obs: vector_query_executed
    Mem->>Obs: memory_fused
    Mem-->>Planner: Fused memory context
    Planner->>Obs: plan_generated
    Planner-->>Exec: AgentPlan
    Exec->>Obs: step_started / tool_called / step_finished
    Exec-->>API: final output or stream chunks
    Exec->>Obs: run_completed
    Exec->>Persist: extract -> chunk -> embed -> upsert
    Persist->>Obs: fact_upserted / profile_updated / vector_upserted
